{"tid":259973,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"請問有無電結他JJ","createTime":"2017-05-27T11:16:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-27T12:17:36.000Z","uid":90663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3b9ef9239f4beeb25ca2aa787ac7f0d950b37477","tid":259973,"uid":90663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T11:16:08.000Z","msg":"利申先，我乜鳩都唔識的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n小弟大概8年前係劏利買左個YAMAHA新手套裝 (YAMAHA EG112C)<br />\n，之後學左一排就無再學。<br />\n而家想學返，打算自學，但枝結他擺左咁耐，D弦生哂銹，仲有舊pick-up(我自己都唔知係咪叫咁既名)都有少少裂開既跡象。<br />\n弦既話我覺得自己都有能力換(應該，我諗，好似係)，但pick-up我就真係唔知要點好。<br />\n上網睇個個都話pick-up好重要，安全起見，我自己都想搵人幫我換，但都係果幾個問題喇：唔知搵邊個/係邊到整，價錢如何，手工如何等等。<br />\n<br />\n敢問各位Ching有咩介紹或者建議?多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7910f33ccdf706130bbafca88ecc0f3cbe898272","tid":259973,"uid":93855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T11:42:57.000Z","msg":"你買個新pickup再拎出去比人整應該仲貴過你枝結他<br />\n買過枝仲好啦 除非你話依枝有感情"},{"pid":"aa7bd3e067e1b46c3601d855f1a80451d900944a","tid":259973,"uid":15287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T12:02:43.000Z","msg":"8年。。<br />\n如果你冇定期護理下個指板我諗啲rosewood收收哋皮<br />\n有冇裂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?有冇蟲捐出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?<br />\n我以前有支捐咗啲白色 嚇到我標屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋你支都放咗咁耐 問題分分鐘唔止pickup<br />\n支結他又唔係貴嘢<br />\n晒錢維修不如買過支新<br />\n<br />\n以前第一支結他同樓主一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a1db631bb3549eb69bc41144f8efe191f2ddbea","tid":259973,"uid":15287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T12:03:20.000Z","msg":"白色蟲 打漏咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4097388f295844f22298828cf5f2ca3b1469341","tid":259973,"uid":51409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T12:04:02.000Z","msg":"買支新既好過"},{"pid":"06631bce74f448ac4ceebfb1aa067c28f606b44e","tid":259973,"uid":90663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T12:07:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你買個新pickup再拎出去比人整應該仲貴過你枝結他<br />\n買過枝仲好啦 除非你話依枝有感情</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為其實我都無咩掂過枝結他，就咁唔要又覺得好浪費"},{"pid":"8e2aea6d3f2f4517b92acc928e54473eb8765b9c","tid":259973,"uid":37078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T12:09:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/199283/page/32?ref=android\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/199283/page/32?ref=android</a><br />\n入黎一齊傾，不停有人答問題"},{"pid":"7f15e69f7911045e4441514612738af73cd17252","tid":259973,"uid":90663,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T12:17:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>8年。。<br />\n如果你冇定期護理下個指板我諗啲rosewood收收哋皮<br />\n有冇裂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?有冇蟲捐出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?<br />\n我以前有支捐咗啲白色 嚇到我標屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋你支都放咗咁耐 問題分分鐘唔止pickup<br />\n支結他又唔係貴嘢<br />\n晒錢維修不如買過支新<br />\n<br />\n以前第一支結他同樓主一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我無護理架，只係無鳩聊果陣會攞出黎調音咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我果枝又無你咁誇張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我長期擺係袋入面既，睇落都仲幾新<br />\n我pickguard果塊膠模都係前幾日先撕走架咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}